                    <div id="question-header" class="grid sm:fd-column">
                        <h1 itemprop="name" class="grid--cell fs-headline1 fl1 ow-break-word mb8"><a href="/questions/108771/what-is-the-difference-between-a-hard-link-and-a-symbolic-link" class="question-hyperlink">What is the difference between a hard link and a symbolic link?</a></h1>

                <div class="ml12 aside-cta grid--cell print:d-none sm:ml0 sm:mb12 sm:order-first sm:as-end">

    <a href="/questions/ask" class="ws-nowrap s-btn s-btn__primary" >
