            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="svg-icon iconStar" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 12.65l-5.29 3.63 1.82-6.15L.44 6.22l6.42-.17L9 0l2.14 6.05 6.42.17-5.1 3.9 1.83 6.16L9 12.65z"/></svg>
