<div class="postcell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">

<p>As the title says, I would like to know the difference between a hard link and a soft link created by the command <code>ln</code>. The command <code>man ln</code> does provide information, but does not sufficiently answer my question.</p>

<p>Also, it would be nice if someone could provide a setting where hard link might be preferable over a symbolic link.</p>
    </div>

